&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have an MS/PhD in Computer Science, ML, or related field, or equivalent experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess strong programming skills, especially in Python&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have experience with ML model training and experimentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a track record of implementing ML research&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate strong analytical skills for interpreting experimental results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have experience with ML metrics and evaluation frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excel at turning research ideas into working code&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Can identify and resolve practical implementation challenges&lt;/li&gt;
